{
  "text": "The study of the effectiveness of the cuboid segmentation algorithm in [CITATION_1] , which we coined as CSeg'17 for the rest of this paper, is on how this algorithm contributes to image retrieval performance. In this paper, we study the effectiveness of CSeg'17 by focusing on the quality of segmentation. From our study, we have identified the following limitations in CSeg'17:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "29043518"
